title: New Nintendo Switch! - Kinda Funny Games Daily 03.04.21
description:
Parris Lilly joins Greg to talk about Bloomberg's report on the new Switch, Avengers making some dumb and smart decisions, and more! 

Follow Parris: https://twitter.com/vicious696

00:00:00 - Start
00:04:15 - Housekeeping
The Blessing Show has a new episode on youtube.com/kindafunnygames! It’s all about puzzle games!
The Kinda Funny Podcast is live with the new voice of Cleveland on Family Guy, Arif Zahir.
MCU IN REVIEW RETURNS TOMORROW! WandaVision
Thank you to our Patreon Producers:
Mick @DaNanoBiologist Abrahamson, Black Jack, & Trent Berrie
The Roper Report   -
00:09:39 - New Nintendo Switch Details, Takashi Mochizuki and Sohee Kim
00:17:45 - With the news of a Switch 2 potentially releasing this year, I have to ask, will Horizon get positioned against BOTW again? - Best Friends Q:Branddnh
00:21:39 - Super Nintendo World on Hold for 2 Years, Joe Skrebbels @ IGN
00:24:38 - Avengers is making dumb and smart decisions XP Rework
00:40:46 - Guilty Gear Strive Delayed
00:46:30 -  Ad
00:51:03 - Out today
00:56:20 - You‘re Wrong
Tomorrow’s Hosts:Blessing and Michael Higham
